        <item>
            <title>Tim Cook: 中国青年才俊令我印象深刻，很高兴 Apple 产品助青年实现梦想</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/tim-cook-said-chinese-teenagers-impression-deep/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tim-cook-said-chinese-teenagers-impression-deep</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/tim-cook-said-chinese-teenagers-impression-deep/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 11:30:12 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299360</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 公司行政总裁 Tim Cook 今日透过微博发文，赞扬中国青年才俊的杰出表现。他表示，看到 MacBook Pro、Mac Studio 及 Apple Vision Pro 等产品协助这些年轻人追逐梦想，感到十分欣慰。发文附有与青年代表的合照，气氛轻松愉快。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032540840-621x580.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032540840-621x580.jpg 621w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032540840.jpg 749w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 621px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/5524254784">Tim Cook@Weibo</a></p><p>Tim Cook 在微博中具体提到，中国青年才俊利用 Apple 产品展现创意与才华，例如用 MacBook Pro 追踪风暴、以 Mac Studio 运行大型语言模型，甚至透过 Apple Vision Pro 教授物理学。他强调，这些实例充分展示 Apple 技术如何成为年轻人实现理想的重要工具。青年代表与 Tim Cook 交流时现场演示产品应用，最后更一同合影留念。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4ziwlp-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4ziwlp-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4ziwlp.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/5524254784">Tim Cook@Weibo</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299366" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zhf1a-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zhf1a-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zhf1a.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zhf1a-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/5524254784">Tim Cook@Weibo</a></p><p>Tim Cook 于 3 月 23 日抵达北京，展开 2025 年首次中国行程。除与青年才俊互动外，他亦参与了在钓鱼台国宾馆举行的中国发展高层论坛 2025 年年会，期间被问及是否使用中国 AI 应用 DeepSeek，他回答：「当然，很棒！」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zi89q-550x580.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zi89q-550x580.jpg 550w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/0061rd1cgy1hzt4zi89q.jpg 853w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 550px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/u/5524254784">Tim Cook@Weibo</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/25/tim-cook-said-chinese-teenagers-impression-deep/fun-tech/">Tim Cook: 中国青年才俊令我印象深刻，很高兴 Apple 产品助青年实现梦想</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
